            <h2>Best Practices for Staying Safe Online</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Use strong, unique passwords for each of your accounts.</li>
                <li>Enable two-factor authentication (2FA) wherever possible.</li>
                <li>Be cautious of suspicious emails and links.</li>
                <li>Keep your software and systems updated.</li>
                <li>Regularly back up your data.</li>
            </ul>
